          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Renters Fairness and Equality Act</strong></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow a tax deduction of all rent paid paid or accrued on the principal residence of a taxpayer, but denies such deduction if the assessed or appraised value of the residence exceeds $1 million. </p>]]></text>
